{"prompt": "Create an informative blog for a health and fitness coach. The layout should feature a bright apple green.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>FitLife Coaching</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #8FBC8F; /* DarkSeaGreen, a pleasant apple green */\n            --secondary-color: #98FB98; /* PaleGreen, lighter shade */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #F5FFFA; /* MintCream, very light off-white */\n            --header-footer-bg: #66CDAA; /* MediumAquaMarine, for contrast */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #8FBC8F 3px solid;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        header .branding {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 15px;\n        }\n\n        header .branding img {\n            height: 50px;\n            width: auto;\n        }\n\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            box-shadow: inset 0 0 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n            list-style: none;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(143, 188, 143, 0.7), rgba(152, 251, 152, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x400/8FBC8F/FFFFFF?text=Fitness+Motivation') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 400px;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .hero-section h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .blog-posts {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .post-card {\n            background: #ffffff;\n            border: 1px solid #dddddd;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .post-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 1